<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title> Activation Email </title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html"; charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type = "text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color: #222222;
        }
        a{
            color:#000;
            text-decoration:  none;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        /*Layout*/
        .email-wrapper{
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header{
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-body{
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-footer{
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        /*Buttons*/
        .button{
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1> Welcome to INIT! </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p> Hello <%= user.name %>, </p>
            <p> Thank you for registering with INIT! </p>
            <p> To activate your account, please use the following activation code: </p>
            <h2> <%= user.activationCode %> </h2>
            <p>Please enter this code on activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for a INIT account, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p> Regards, </p>
            <p> The INIT Team </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com"> INIT </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/contact"> Contact Us </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/privacy"> Privacy Policy </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/terms"> Terms of Service </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/unsubscribe"> Unsubscribe </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/feedback"> Feedback </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/faq"> FAQ </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/about"> About Us </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/careers"> Careers </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/press"> Press </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/blog"> Blog </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/support"> Support </a> </p>
            <p> <a href="https://init.com/developers"> Developers </a> </p>
            <p> If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:info@init.org.in">info@init.org.in</a> </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>